  <h2>A Fast Sale Can Simplify the Division of Assets</h2>
  <p>When a marriage ends, the family home often becomes a significant point of contention. A quick cash sale eliminates months of uncertainty, removes the property from the equation, and gives both parties a clear number to divide — without waiting on buyer financing or open houses.</p>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-box">
